# RECAFCO AuditFlow ISO — Root environment reference
# Each app/package has its own .env file. See:
#   packages/db/.env.example       — PostgreSQL connection (Prisma)
#   apps/api/.env.example           — NestJS API variables
#   apps/web/.env.example           — Next.js frontend variables

# Quick start: copy each .env.example to .env (or .env.local for web)
# and update credentials to match your local PostgreSQL setup.
